<div class="about-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Sloop</h1>

        <div class="card shadow-sm p-4 mb-4">
          <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Our Mission</h2>
          <p>Sloop was created with a clear mission: to redefine travel by offering Sloopy, unique circular itineraries tailored to your preferences. Rooted in sustainability, our platform enables you to explore responsibly while making every journey enjoyable and impactful.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card shadow-sm p-4 mb-4">
          <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Our Story</h2>
          <p>Founded in 2024, Sloop is the product of a collaboration between passionate travelers and tech innovators. Inspired by the need for meaningful, eco-friendly exploration, we developed Sloopy to help people rediscover the joy of travel while respecting the planet.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card shadow-sm p-4 mb-4">
          <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Our Technology</h2>
          <p>At Sloop, we leverage cutting-edge AI technology to craft personalized itineraries tailored to your unique preferences and travel habits. Our intelligent system analyzes your interests and suggests the perfect Sloopy for you, making each journey truly your own.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card shadow-sm p-4 mb-4 values-section">
          <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Our Values</h2>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
              <h3 class="h5">Sustainability</h3>
              <p>We ensure every Sloopy minimizes environmental impact by promoting green choices.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
              <h3 class="h5">Personalization</h3>
              <p>Every Sloopy is crafted to reflect your unique preferences and interests.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
              <h3 class="h5">Discovery</h3>
              <p>Sloopy encourages you to rediscover familiar places and uncover hidden gems.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card shadow-sm p-4 team-card">
          <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Our Team</h2>
          <p>Our passionate team of explorers-tech enthusiasts is dedicated to improving your experience with Sloop. We work tirelessly to create itineraries that inspire and respect the planet, ensuring every adventure is unforgettable.</p>

          <div class="team-members mt-4">
            <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
              <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-4">
                <div class="team-member">
                  <%= image_tag "Antoine.png", class: "team-avatar mb-2" %>
                  <h3 class="h5 member-name">Antoine</h3>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-4">
                <div class="team-member">
                  <%= image_tag "Daisy.png", class: "team-avatar mb-2" %>
                  <h3 class="h5 member-name">Daisy</h3>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-4">
                <div class="team-member">
                  <%= image_tag "JR.png", class: "team-avatar mb-2" %>
                  <h3 class="h5 member-name">JR</h3>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-4">
                <div class="team-member">
                  <%= image_tag "Youss.png", class: "team-avatar mb-2" %>
                  <h3 class="h5 member-name">Youss</h3>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
